{"tid":2052310,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"藍到發黑嘅兒童瑜伽studio","createTime":"2020-06-05T12:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T07:36:36.000Z","uid":228343,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"48e1b357e8b58842f810efb750aa52ae1c990bd6","tid":2052310,"uid":228343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:18:23.000Z","msg":"純粹睇唔過眼，條八婆又成日接觸小朋友<br />\n學野都要睇清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CyUD9Pm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCyUD9Pm.png&h=4789021f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後有人留言回應，佢又扮傻話自己當年細唔知禁多野，要請教人地，但佢下一句已經表明緊自己立場，駁返人。<br />\n<br />\n講到自己好似唔去日本咁，相簿都幾多日本之旅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mt8Q0Zh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMt8Q0Zh.jpg&h=fe2495a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RH3JBxC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRH3JBxC.jpg&h=55232fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>（黃嘅人我打格左）</strong><br />\n仲講到出黎遊行嘅人搞到香港咁同唔知做緊乜咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HFCqPS8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHFCqPS8.png&h=9b194077&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cBZQgya.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcBZQgya.png&h=194848ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P3MWb6y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP3MWb6y.png&h=71f46fad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBJagyd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBJagyd.png&h=924b098e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c56bcfba09aa261171fe8c3ef5515671d8492970","tid":2052310,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:20:13.000Z","msg":"<im